headline: Paramount (PSKY): Buy, Sell, or Hold Post Q3 Earnings?
summary: Over the past six months, Paramount has been a great trade, beating the S&P 500 by 20.7%. Its stock price has climbed to $15.75, representing a healthy 33.7% increase. This run-up might have investors contemplating their next move.
